# Install Terraform

## Steps to Install

1. With the terminal open, use these commands with Brew (Software installed in last step) to install Terform:

brew tap hashicorp/tap

brew install hashicorp/tap/terraform

2. Check to see if Terraform actually installed run this command

terraform --version

3. Now log in to terraform using this command 

terraform login

4. Type yes

5. In browser that just popped up, you will be asked to create a token. Create the token with a memorable name and copy the token.

6. Go to the terminal and paste that code in there.

Welcome to Terraform Cloud.

Proceed on to the next step to learn how to code with Terraform. 
